    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35224598_6_2018-2078",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2018-2078",
      "markText": "魏晋时代是中国历史上最自由、火热生命积聚最多的热血时代。不管谁做皇帝，天下都是大名士的天下，上层门阀世家是社会的中坚力量",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35224598&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2018&rangeEnd=2078",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38b321f072197c1638b3888?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2018&rangeEnd=2078"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35224598_22_7368-7437",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "7368-7437",
      "markText": "一九四九年，张先生将收藏尽数捐献国家。我们今日所见，都是先生经过战乱贫穷，散尽家财，一生的心血。在张先生眼中，这种结局才是国宝最好的归宿。",
      "totalCount": 518,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35224598&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=7368&rangeEnd=7437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38b321f072197c1638b3888?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=7368&rangeEnd=7437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35224598_6_5505-5552",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5505-5552",
      "markText": "魏晋人的可贵可爱之处便在于此，超脱礼法，不在乎个人的过往出身甚至信仰，尊重个人价值与品格之美。",
      "totalCount": 425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35224598&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5505&rangeEnd=5552",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38b321f072197c1638b3888?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5505&rangeEnd=5552"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35224598_13_11193-11279",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "11193-11279",
      "markText": "“二战”后，为了感谢中国军队在缅甸帮助英军解除日军之围，英国给了中国两个选择：第一，大英博物馆将这幅画归还给中国政府；第二，英国送给中国一艘潜水艇。最终，中国选择了潜水艇。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35224598&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=11193&rangeEnd=11279",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38b321f072197c1638b3888?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=11193&rangeEnd=11279"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35224598_30_3221-3234",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "3221-3234",
      "markText": "故宫六百年，承蒙先生看顾。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35224598&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=3221&rangeEnd=3234",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38b321f072197c1638b3888?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=3221&rangeEnd=3234"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35224598_6_1670-1712",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1670-1712",
      "markText": "几千年来，能在没有一本真迹存世的情况下，依然笑傲群雄的书法家，只有“书圣”王羲之了。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35224598&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1670&rangeEnd=1712",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/38b321f072197c1638b3888?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1670&rangeEnd=1712"
    },
    {
